# Storage Provider Configuration
# Add these environment variables to your .env file to enable storage integration

# Google Drive
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret

# Microsoft OneDrive
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=your_microsoft_client_id
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_microsoft_client_secret
MICROSOFT_TENANT_ID=common

# Dropbox
DROPBOX_CLIENT_ID=your_dropbox_app_key
DROPBOX_CLIENT_SECRET=your_dropbox_app_secret

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy these variables to your .env file
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 3. Set up OAuth applications for each provider:
#    - Google: https://console.cloud.google.com/
#    - Microsoft: https://portal.azure.com/
#    - Dropbox: https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps